{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act34side_level_act34side_02_end","storyGroup":"act34side","storySort":5,"storyDependence":"act34side_level_act34side_02_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"BP-2","storyName":"评议式迎接","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"在深海猎人计划曾经的技术顾问布兰都斯的帮助下，歌蕾蒂娅等人证明了自己的清白与安全，但乌尔比安的嫌疑却难以洗脱。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act34side/level_act34side_02_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act34side_02","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":3,"next":5,"characters":["军团长官","歌蕾蒂娅","斯卡蒂","幽灵鲨","科学院研究员","？？？","乌尔比安","布兰都斯","克莱门莎","技术院科研人员"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_bg_51_g6_aegirarena.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loading_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_sys_loading_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1400_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":10},{"type":"dialogue","name":"军团长官","text":"歌蕾蒂娅执政官，您认为问题并不在于那场战役本身？","id":11,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_1400_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"是的。详细的作战部署此刻正投影在各位面前，如果其中存在我没能注意到的纰漏，你们每个人都有义务指出。","id":13,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1400_1#1$1","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"军团长官","text":"不，我对具体的作战部署没有疑问。结合当时的认知条件，那无疑是最合理的作战部署。","id":15,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_1400_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"军团长官","text":"但我希望知道，现在的您会如何评判当时的认知条件？","id":16,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_1400_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#5","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"必须承认，阿戈尔当时对海嗣的认知存在严重的缺陷......","id":18,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/ba/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_5.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":19},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":20},{"type":"charslot","id":21},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1","id":22},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"char_263_skadi#4","id":23},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":24},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"char_263_skadi#4","focus":"r","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"这些人想说什么？","id":26,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2d/Avg_char_263_skadi_4.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1","focus":"l","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"以前还在阿戈尔的时候，你就不喜欢想太多，你还是不习惯那些人的思考方式。","id":28,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"他们对我们没有恶意，他们只是在寻求必要的事实。","id":29,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"寻找所有可能的缺陷，质疑所有完美的成果。然后，真实与美，还有正确的道路，将在最激烈的争论中彰显自身。","id":30,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"一切交给剑鱼吧。","id":31,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"要是不想听，就闭着眼睛睡一会儿。","id":32,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":33},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":34},{"type":"charslot","id":35},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":36},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......综上，五年前那次战争设计最大的失误，就是没能为我们的认知缺陷留出余地。","id":38,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"在泰拉的真相被揭开之前，我们需要承认自己对海嗣的认知总会存在缺陷，我们的战争设计必须将其考虑在内。","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1400_1#1$1","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"军团长官","text":"同意。您刚刚得出的结论，应当被用于审视未来可能诞生的各项作战计划。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_1400_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"军团长官","text":"能与您一同反思一场已经被尘封的战役，并得出有效的结论，是我的荣幸，歌蕾蒂娅执政官。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c0/Avg_avg_npc_1400_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1397_1#1$1","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科学院研究员","text":"不过，除了五年前的那场战役......","id":44,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1397_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科学院研究员","text":"还有更加现实的问题值得我们担心。","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1397_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科学院研究员","text":"根据体检报告，您、斯卡蒂、劳伦缇娜，三位都发生了不容忽视的身体异变。","id":46,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1397_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科学院研究员","text":"我无意质疑各位对国家的忠诚，但我需要知道海嗣基因对各位的同化，会对各位接下来的行动产生怎样的影响。","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1397_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科学院研究员","text":"请原谅我这么发问。","id":48,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1397_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科学院研究员","text":"弥利亚留姆很快就要完成对所有巢穴的定位，在那之后，海嗣将在第Ⅳ级武器的作用下被驱离，航道正式开启。","id":49,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1397_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科学院研究员","text":"在这个时间点上，深海猎人，是否会成为阿戈尔的敌人、你们自己的敌人？","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1397_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":51},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":52},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.6","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"1","id":53},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":54},{"type":"charslot","id":55},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"200,0","id":56},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","bstart":"0.2","bend":"0.5","focus":"m","id":57},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":58},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"对阿戈尔来说，失控的猎人比海嗣本身更加危险。","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"深海猎人，就像是阿戈尔的反面。他们诞生于阿戈尔最卑劣的伤口，阿戈尔怜悯他们，也畏惧他们。","id":61},{"type":"dialog","id":62},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":63},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","focus":"n","id":64},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"66","text":"深海猎人，乌尔比安，对吧？"}},"values":[],"id":65},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":66},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"68","text":"按理说，你更应该在底下接受质询。"}},"values":[],"id":67},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":68,"end":75},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","duration":"1","focus":"m","id":69},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":70},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","afrom":"0","ato":"0","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你比我想象中要冷静很多，也知道我的身份。","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"看来歌蕾蒂娅在陆地上建立的信任关系，并不只是对那位医生一人。","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我没有在之前的任何一次行动中见过你。你不是伊比利亚的审判官，也不是岛民。","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"那位罗德岛的医生将你带到阿戈尔，却又有意隐藏你的身份。","id":75,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":76},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":77},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"79","text":"我只是凯尔希的同僚。"},"2":{"id":"79","text":"我和她同属于罗德岛。"}},"values":[],"id":78},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":79,"end":82},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"随你怎么定性自己。","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"总之，你能帮到猎人们。","id":82,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":83},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":84},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"86","text":"有事为什么不直接找斯卡蒂？"},"2":{"id":"89","text":"有事为什么不直接找幽灵鲨？"},"3":{"id":"94","text":"有事为什么不直接找歌蕾蒂娅？"}},"values":[],"id":85},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":86,"end":88},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"斯卡蒂不太擅长这样的事情。","id":88},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":89,"end":93},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"你是说劳伦缇娜？","id":91},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1","id":92},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"她不太擅长这样的事情。","id":93},{"type":"predicate","references":["3"],"id":94,"end":96},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"现在并不是合适的时机。","id":96,"end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2","3"],"id":97},{"type":"dialog","id":98},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":99},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"101","text":"你不信任猎人们？"}},"values":[],"id":100},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":101,"end":109},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#2$1","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"恰恰相反，我信任她们，而且太过了解她们。","id":103},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"斯卡蒂的行动快过思考，劳伦缇娜清醒的时日尚浅，最终决定一切的人只会是歌蕾蒂娅。","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"此前我已经向她分享过许多情报，她应该有了警惕。她并非不清楚自己会遭遇多少限制，但仍然选择回到阿戈尔。","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"她太急于回到熟悉的环境，殊不知自己已经被摆在了最显眼的位置，一切可信任的和不可信任的都有十足的权力来审视她。","id":107},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"现在并不是深海猎人返乡的最好时机，这是一场豪赌。","id":109,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":110},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":111},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"113","text":"既然如此，你为什么还要潜入这座城市？"},"2":{"id":"113","text":"看来你还是很关心猎人们。"}},"values":[],"id":112},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":113,"end":124},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"歌蕾蒂娅她们的处境不容乐观。","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"与我不同，她们三人虽然接受了改造，却没有参与深海猎人计划最核心的研发工作。她们很难解释清楚自己身体的异变。","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"我会告诉你一些相关的信息，必要的时候，我需要你想办法为歌蕾蒂娅解围。事后，再向她传达我的提醒。","id":117},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"至于更多的事情——","id":119},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":120},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"或许，各位可以听我说两句。","id":122},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"......布兰都斯。他也来到了这里？","id":124,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":125},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":126},{"type":"charslot","id":127},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":128},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"布兰都斯？","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":131},{"type":"dialog","id":132},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$newhope01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_newhope01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":133,"musicid":1},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":134},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","duration":"1","id":135},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"每次都是这样，以前在研究所的时候，你也好，乌尔比安也好，总是趁我打盹的时候和研究员们吵起来。","id":137,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#1$1","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"顾问，你的意见确实会很有参考价值。","id":139,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"不胜荣幸。","id":141,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"我曾是深海猎人计划的技术顾问，负责改造实验中的基因嵌合研究。换句话说......","id":143,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#5$1","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"此时此刻，我是这座城市最了解深海猎人的人。","id":145,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"歌蕾蒂娅、劳伦缇娜、斯卡蒂，她们在干燥的环境待了太久，其间依然频繁地进行战斗，她们的身体情况确实不容乐观。","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"multiline","name":"布兰都斯","text":"各位的担心很有道理。但我的答案是，","id":147},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","id":148},{"type":"multiline","name":"布兰都斯","text":"不会——","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"她们并不会变成海嗣。","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":151},{"type":"text","text":"寂静。","id":152},{"type":"text","text":"布兰都斯清了清嗓子。","id":153},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"我尽量说得简单些。","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4e/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"我们都知道，海嗣基因在寻常生物体内会展现出异常的性状控制力，不可逆地抹消该生物的本来属性。","id":157,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"我们在深海猎人身上尽可能地延长着这种海嗣化的过程，直到它远远长于猎人的自然寿命。","id":158,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"但后来，技术院的研究取得了关键性进展。在猎人们出发去斩杀“初生”前，我们为他们每人都安排了一台“自适应接点”手术。","id":159,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"“自适应接点”被安置在人类基因与海嗣基因的嵌合处，它能帮助深海猎人对海嗣基因保持更密切的“监视”。","id":160,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"一旦海嗣基因表现出异常的性状控制力，“自适应接点”就会催使猎人的身体进行抵抗，防止海嗣基因夺取控制权。","id":161,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"尽管猎人们的“自适应接点”已经在未经维护的情况下运行了五年，难免会有老化，但她们如今的异变都尚在预期范围之内。","id":162,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1397_1#1$1","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科学院研究员","text":"顾问，根据深海猎人研究所当年的记录，“自适应接点”手术曾经出现过一场手术事故。","id":164,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1397_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":165},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":166},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.6","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"0.5","id":167},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":168},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"3","id":169},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#2$1","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"那场事故发生在......乌尔比安身上。","id":171,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"但记录应该也有说明，经过多次临床验证，我们已证明那场事故没有产生任何不良影响。","id":173,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"我可以对此负责，也愿意为此接受质询。","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"既然深海猎人回到了阿戈尔，那么她们的身体状况就是可控的。","id":175,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1397_1#1$1","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科学院研究员","text":"听起来，您已经有了控制猎人身体异变的可行手段？","id":177,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1397_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"城内就有一间闲置已久的深海猎人研究所，可以被重新启用。之后，我可以亲自为她们进行“自适应接点”的维护。","id":179,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1397_1#1$1","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科学院研究员","text":"那么，乌尔比安呢？","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1397_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"......","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1397_1#1$1","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科学院研究员","text":"那位至今不愿回归阿戈尔的深海猎人，我们该如何确保他不会堕落成海嗣？","id":185,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1397_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"科学院研究员","text":"还是说，我们担心的事情已经发生了？","id":186,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1397_1$1.png"},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":187},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.6","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"0.5","id":188},{"type":"dialog","id":189},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":190},{"type":"charslot","id":191},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":192},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":193},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"195","text":"话题的焦点突然转移到了你身上。"},"2":{"id":"195","text":"听起来你很危险。"}},"values":[],"id":194},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":195,"end":199},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"哼。","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"他们的怀疑很合理。","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"对超出掌控的事物保持十二分的警惕，是常识，也是来之不易的教训。","id":199,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":200},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":201},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"203","text":"怀疑你的不止场上的那些人。"},"2":{"id":"203","text":"我也好奇你隐藏行迹的原因。"}},"values":[],"id":202},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":203},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"205","text":"你潜入城市，真的只是出于对猎人的关心？"}},"values":[],"id":204},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":205,"end":209},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#3$1","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"斯图提斐拉沉没之前，我曾向歌蕾蒂娅分享我的发现——海嗣中存在着不止一只类似伊莎玛拉的超级个体——“初生”。","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"而此时此刻，新的“初生”已经“松动”，祂，或祂们，苏醒在即。","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"不确定数量，不确定时间......但是很近。","id":209,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":210},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":211},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"213","text":"......"}},"values":[],"id":212},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":213,"end":218},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"海嗣向陆地的迁徙与之相关。这段时间，我深入了足够多的巢穴，海嗣的反应共同传递出某种......危机感。","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"或许连如今的海洋都不足以供养这场觉醒？新“神”的苏醒，是另一场陆地人口中的大静谧，还是其他形式的海洋灾难？","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"这场浩大的迁徙与阿戈尔的航道计划几乎同步发生，那么，弥利亚留姆在其中到底处于怎样的位置？","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乌尔比安","text":"这些是否足够让我来到这座城市？","id":218,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":219},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":220},{"type":"charslot","id":221},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":222},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","id":223},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"技术院科研人员","text":"海嗣固然能在本能的驱动下独立繁衍，但它们源于“初生”，不可能违背最基本的生物性。","id":225,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1396_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"技术院科研人员","text":"换言之，即使那只“初生”的死亡没有遏止海嗣的进化，也不至于使它们爆发式地涌现出前所未见的特质。","id":226,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1396_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"您似乎忽视了我在任务书里提到的最新情报。","id":228,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"技术院科研人员","text":"“复数的初生”，这样的解释很合理，可我对乌尔比安的质疑恰恰来源于此。","id":230,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1396_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"技术院科研人员","text":"计划周详的行动以失败告终，幸存的三位猎人随着海浪来到陌生的陆地，与那位在巢穴中滞留到最后的猎人重逢。","id":231,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1396_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"技术院科研人员","text":"“海中存在‘复数的初生’”，乌尔比安带来的这一情报不仅具有颠覆性，而且非常“有效”。","id":232,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1396_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"技术院科研人员","text":"它恰如其分地解释了为什么明明你们完成了作战目标，却催生了海嗣更大的异动。它回应了所有人的疑问。","id":233,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1396_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"您对这一情报的疑问在于？","id":235,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1396_1#1$1","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"技术院科研人员","text":"这样恰到好处的解释，要么是唯一的真相，要么是针对所有疑问设计出的答案。","id":237,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1396_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":238},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":239},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"1","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"0.5","id":240},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":241},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"3","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"技术院科研人员","text":"是否采信乌尔比安传递给您的情报，会对我们接下来的战争设计产生重大的影响。","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1396_1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"技术院科研人员","text":"既然乌尔比安还活着，那么确认他的行迹与状态，甚至与他当面对证，就是最直接有效的验证方式。","id":244,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6d/Avg_avg_npc_1396_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"......","id":246,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#2$1","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"布兰都斯顾问，你已经沉默了许久。","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"关于乌尔比安的情况，你有什么想要补充的吗？","id":249,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"我知道你与乌尔比安师出同门，甚至你加入深海猎人计划，也是出于对乌尔比安的信任——你一开始并不赞成这项计划。","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"但我同样信任你作为阿戈尔人的专业与德行，你不必刻意回避什么。","id":251,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"......","id":253,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0b/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#5$1","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"执政官阁下，我只能说，我必须对今天在这场评议会中说过的每一句话负责。","id":255,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"乌尔比安......我不会故意进行任何有利于他的假设，也不想给出任何不利于他的猜想。","id":256,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#2$1","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"仅此而已——","id":258,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_npc_1381_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":259},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":260},{"type":"charslot","id":261},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":262},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":263},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"265","text":"看来你和那位顾问的关系不错。"},"2":{"id":"265","text":"原来再冷酷的人也有这样的朋友。"}},"values":[],"id":264},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":265,"end":268},{"type":"text","text":"乌尔比安没有回应你。场上的质询仍在继续，但布兰都斯不再说话，他突然抬起头看向你所在的方向，像是感应到了什么。","id":266},{"type":"text","text":"隔着大半个斗智场，你对上了他那双有些疲惫的眼睛。","id":267},{"type":"text","text":"他明显注意到了什么，坐在他身侧的执政官，以及相邻的几个阿戈尔人都捕捉到了那一瞬的异样，部分人的目光追了过来。","id":268,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":269},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"271","text":"......"},"2":{"id":"271","text":"呃......"}},"values":[],"id":270},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":271,"end":272},{"type":"text","text":"你侧过身，不知何时，身旁的座位已经空了。","id":272,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":273},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"275","text":"我？我只是个旁观的陆上人而已。"},"2":{"id":"275","text":"不好意思，我打扰到你们了吗？"},"3":{"id":"275","text":"我也需要发表意见吗？"}},"values":[],"id":274},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":275,"end":293},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":276},{"type":"charslot","id":277},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":278},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#2$1","duration":"0.5","id":279},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"通过这场评议会，我们已经得出了充足的结论。","id":281,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#9$1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"歌蕾蒂娅、斯卡蒂、劳伦缇娜，以及其他深海猎人，为阿戈尔付出了巨大的牺牲，也做出了伟大的贡献。","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"时隔五年，我们仍有机会从她们的见闻与经验中生发出新的思考，这是阿戈尔的荣幸。","id":284,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"现在，她们证明了自己的清白与安全，证明了她们在航道计划进行至此的紧要关头回归，不是威胁，而是助力。","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"然而，与此同时，无数疑点聚焦在另一位幸存的深海猎人，乌尔比安身上。","id":286,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"出于不可知的原因隐匿踪迹，并试图影响其余的深海猎人——这些行为显著违背了他身为深海猎人的责任。","id":287,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"根据现有的信息，我们无法确定他究竟怀着何种动机，意欲达成何种目的，甚至连他现在是否还能被称为阿戈尔人都未可知。","id":288,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"乌尔比安必须尽快被找到。即使他真如同歌蕾蒂娅所说的一样不怀恶意，也必须接受质询，以洗清自己身上的重重嫌疑。","id":289,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#1$1","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"疑惑已经得到解答的各位，你们可以离场了。尚有疑问的人，质询可以继续。","id":291,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#3$1","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"歌蕾蒂娅执政官，你还有什么想要补充的吗？","id":293,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":294},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":295},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_51_i05.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.4","yScale":"1.4","id":296},{"type":"imagetween","yTo":"0","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"100","block":"false","id":297},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":298},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":299},{"type":"text","text":"斗智场中央的珊瑚状终端缓缓合拢、收缩、下沉，最终没入地面以下。水纹荡漾的场地平坦而空旷，仿佛是要容纳一场戏剧演出。","id":300},{"type":"text","text":"场地中央，唯有歌蕾蒂娅一人。","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"我已经告诉了你们我所知的一切。","id":302,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"我对评议会的结果没有意见，对乌尔比安的嫌疑，也不持任何异议。","id":303,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"text","text":"已经陆续有人离场，他们在出口转身，默契地向歌蕾蒂娅颔首致意。","id":304},{"type":"text","text":"余下的听众仍在发问。歌蕾蒂娅应对着她知道或不知道答案的问题。","id":305},{"type":"text","text":"穹顶投下的水纹与萦绕场地的光纹相交织，却没能在歌蕾蒂娅的脸上映照出任何表情。","id":306},{"type":"dialog","id":307},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":308},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_51_i05.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","id":309},{"type":"imagetween","yTo":"0","xScaleTo":"1","yScaleTo":"1","duration":"100","block":"false","id":310},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"哪怕我是个阿戈尔人，有时候也搞不懂这种状况。","id":312,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"明明上一秒还在唇枪舌剑针锋相对，下一秒又在感谢歌蕾蒂娅对阿戈尔的付出。","id":313,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"他们是真诚的。科学要求人们把情感与事实分开，而他们确实做到了。","id":314,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"我当然知道这些人是真诚的，我只是......唉，算了。","id":315,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"三队长目前也只是受到怀疑，剑鱼、博士和凯尔希都会想办法的。","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"接下来我们去哪儿？","id":317,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"等剑鱼来找我们吧。这场评议会一时半会儿还没法完全结束。唉。","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"你怎么也突然叹气？","id":319,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"剑鱼以前常去当时那座城市的斗智场看戏剧演出，除非有战斗安排，否则一场不落。我有时候会跟着她一起去。","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"二队长她......","id":321,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"剑鱼的艺术造诣挺高的，据说是被她母亲培养出来的。","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"但是和一般的观众不一样，她喜欢坐在最高最远的位子上，搞得我每次都得和她分开坐。","id":323,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"为什么？","id":324,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"在她看来，保持适当的距离，就可以尽可能地排除干扰。忽略一些场地上的细节，反而能更好地体会故事本身。","id":325,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"而此刻，她自己却成了站在剧场中央的人。","id":326,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"她习惯的距离感被完全消解，她成了被审视、剖析、讨论的对象。在那个位置，没有人可以保持从容。","id":327,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"鲨鱼，我突然也明白自己刚刚因为什么叹气了。","id":328,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"因为什么？","id":329,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"直到此刻，我才确认我们真的回到了阿戈尔。","id":330,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":331},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":332},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":333},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":334},{"type":"image","id":335},{"type":"charslot","id":336}],"characters":["军团长官","歌蕾蒂娅","斯卡蒂","幽灵鲨","科学院研究员","？？？","乌尔比安","布兰都斯","克莱门莎","技术院科研人员"]}